<template>
  <main
    @onDataIsLoaded="test"
    data-depth="0.2"
  >
    <v-sheet
      id="scrolling-techniques-2"
      :height="screenHeight"
    >
      <slot/>
    </v-sheet>
  </main>
</template>

<script>
export default {
  name: "content",
  props: {
    pageName: {
      type: String,
      required: true
    },
  },
  computed: {
    screenHeight: () => screen.height
  },
  methods: {
    test(eventName) {
      console.log("test 2");
      this.$emit(eventName);
    }
  }
}
</script>
